schools.name: Veterans Park Academy For The Arts

data.description: 4 bedroom 3 bath POOL home with water slide sits on almost a HALF ACRE. This home features a phenomenal layout with tons of possibilities and potential. Two separate living quarters on each side. Courtyard features an 8ft kidney shaped pool. This home is perfect for entertaining family and friends. The home is also equipped with two AC units and two hot water heaters (One for each side), extra parking on the oversized driveway, an oversized garage, a room for extra storage, and home is completely fenced. This is a great Location! Conveniently located close to medical facilities, shopping, restaurants and easy access to Fort Myers.
